# FILE: halabStore.desc
# ROLE: High-Speed Product Catalog & Discovery Hub
# VIBE: Scientific Marketplace / 90-Degree Grid / High-Contrast

## 1. THE UNIFIED NAVIGATION SIDEBAR
- **CATEGORIES:** [ 💻 Hardware ], [ 📐 Engineering Gear ], [ 🏥 Medical Kits ], [ 👕 Platform Merch ].
- **FILTER HUD:**
    - **PRICE RANGE:** Slider for SYP.
    - **SOURCE TOGGLE:** [ 🏠 منصة ] | [ 🤝 وسيط ].
    - **AVAILABILITY:** [ ⚡ تسليم فوري ] (Immediate) | [ 📦 طلب مسبق ] (Pre-order).

## 2. THE PRODUCT CARD (GRID ITEM)
- **TOP-LAYER BADGES:** - **Left:** [ % خصم للطالب ] (Red Background / White Text).
    - **Right:** [ 🏠 منصة ] (Cyan) OR [ 🤝 وسيط ] (Amber).
- **IMAGE AREA:** Transparent PNG of product; 1:1 Aspect Ratio.
- **PRICING BLOCK:** - `Original_Price` (Strikethrough Gray).
    - `Student_Price` (Bold White / Primary).
- **ACTION:** [ 💳 حجز ] (Quick Reserve) | [ 💬 تفاصيل ] (Link to Subpage).

## 3. THE "EMPTY SEARCH" NODE
- **LOGIC:** If no results found, show a "Request a Product" card.
- **ACTION:** [ 📲 Request Broker ] -> Opens WhatsApp link with pre-filled sourcing info.

---

# FILE: productSubPage.desc
# ROLE: Technical Spec-Sheet & Transaction Terminal
# VIBE: Data-Heavy / Industrial Precision / High-Trust

## 1. THE HERO SPLIT (60/40 Layout)
- **LEFT (GALLERY):** Vertical thumbnail strip + Large Main View with Hover-Zoom.
- **RIGHT (THE ACTION HUB):**
    - **IDENTITY:** Product Title + Unique ID (e.g., #HS-102).
    - **SAVINGS METER:** "You save [X] SYP via HalabUnver."
    - **PRIMARY CTA:** [ 💳 حجز وإتمام الدفع ] -> Triggers 2-hour reservation lock.

## 2. THE LOGISTICS BENTO (Admin-Controlled)
- **SOURCE STATUS:** - [ 🏠 منصة ]: "Owned by platform, in local warehouse."
    - [ 🤝 وسيط ]: "Sourced externally, inspected by HalabUnver."
- **PICKUP/DELIVERY:** Admin-set location (e.g., "Engineering Faculty Gate").
- **TIMELINE:** "Immediate" vs "3-5 Business Days".

## 3. THE TECHNICAL DNA (The Spec Sheet)
- **SPEC_GRID:** Monospace table for CPU, RAM, Weight, Battery Health.
- **ADMIN_NOTE:** Rich-text area for "Staff Review" or "Device History".
- **DOCUMENTATION:** [ 📄 Download Official Datasheet ] (PDF Link).